# Cookbook Backend

Simple Spring Boot backend for recipe endpoints.

## Run Locally

Use these commands (your existing local flow):

1. Compile:

mvn clean compile

2. Start the app:

mvn spring-boot:run

## Run Tests

Run all tests:

mvn test

Or with the Maven wrapper:

./mvnw test

## Compile Check (No Tests)

Use this to quickly verify there are no compilation errors:

mvn clean compile

Or with the Maven wrapper:

./mvnw clean compile